I'm still alive.  Things with the boyfriend (Andrew--just to clarify that) are super fantastic, I am relishing that "being in love" sensation once more, I'm back in school, my job sucks but I am STILL there, I am trying to keep things cool with Tim but they do not seem to be working, I made up with Dan, my birthday is next month, I got a super haircut from jessi, i have renounced fucking punk (as if i ever liked it anyway), i am addicted to myspace, i am thousands of dollars in debt, but mostly life is so good.

I'm happy.  Things with Drew are wonderful. 

Tim is coming back today, I believe. I really have missed him but I know he probably won't ever want to talk to me again.   That kills me.  My first love, my best friend for so long--won't even acknowledge me.  I understand how bad it hurts though, I really do.

Arg work gay that is all.
I'm going away for a while guys.  It was nice knowing you, if I know you at all.

I feel very detached from everyone lately.  I don't know why.  I even feel detached from Tim, and that worries me.  I have been trying so hard to mend things and they seem to be fine but something is not right.  I wish I knew what it was.  I am discontent with everything about my life right now, maybe for just this week, who knows.

Yesterday...or rather this...morning...I was at work until 3:15 am, not nice.  I worked 2-10, was fully intent on going home, then somebody called out.  I am exhausted as fuck, but I have another job interview today at Target.  I doubt they will give me what I am asking for; it is a futile attempt to escape from 711.

The nice thing is, I have the next 4 days off.  The not so nice thing is, I just got paid today, paid both credit card bills and a phonebill, and now I'm broke again.

And Brandon called my phone yesterday.  What the fuck?

To everybody who I didn't call back Friday night/this morning:  I left my phone in the car and was wayyy far away from it, sorry!

I wish I was tired so I could go to fucking bed.

Got sort of drunk at the beach with Drew last night, got home at 6:30, woke up a few hours later, went to work, rinse, repeat.

I have the next three days off.

Somebody hit me up.

The drama is neverending and killing meeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeee arg

I try to be a good friend, I really do, but its never good enough.

Tonight I'm taking it easy.  (Possible) sleepover with the boy, swimming tomorrow (I bought a new string bikini but my boobs don't--fit--into it), who knows what else.

I keep making sort of plans with people and then blowing them off...sorry people.  I don't do these things on purpose, I'm just very...forgetful.  And busy.

I just woke up, I am backing up my entire fucking cd collection onto the computer, it is going to take about ten years.  

Me and Timmeh had a big fight the other day, but things are ok now, or at least better than they were before.  I am stubborn and cruel and I know most of our fights are entirely my fault.  I really need to get my priorities straight and stop taking this wonderful person I have in my life for granted, before he leaves again.

This fall I am going back to school.  I am excited.  It feels like I grow more stupid with each passing day I am away.
i cut all my hair off! what do you think?

so i went to paul's little birthday bash, but there were all these gay kids at dirt's house so i left. i was reading through some super old im's from timmeh about how we used to meet eachother in the middle of the night....sneak into windows...walk to super walmart...when there is this knock on the window right next to the computer. it was both tims, just like old times, and it was super cool. tomorrow i am FINALLY going to the zoo with my lovely boy.

I got my nipples pierced, kind of a spur of the moment thing, but it looks fucking sweet.  Kate and I were supposed to go, but Tim had the money 2 days ago and somehow I ended up just doing it.  It hurt, but not really as bad as I thought it was going to.  I debated on posting pictures, but ultimately decided it seems kinda iffy.

Things are icky today.
I love them (not the huge pictures of my face, the snakebites).

I have snakebites, but my lip is swollen and disgusting and I think this flatback is too short so I'm going to go get it changed today.  It looks hot though.  My manager made me wear a band-aid over it, it hurt and looked gay.

Blahhhh no work today

i just got home and there is a tent in my living room.  what the fuck?

mike and i went to village perks and ate food and talked to the awesome owner, then we went to west melbourne, then we came back and ate more food.  what a productive day.  i lost money and gas all for the pursuit of food.  no, it was fun though.  i had a good time.  

me + tim + ariel + dirtay + saturday = double date at the movies?  sounds fun to me.

aghhh i'm so full.

I've been running into so many people lately, its crazy.  I saw Black Jeff at 711 tonight while I was working, then I ran into Charles at Hess, and Crust came by yesterday.  Also saw Alex and Colby from high school.  Talked to Dan tonight, he went to a gay bar, that is funny as hell.  

Tim got a new tattoo, it is pretty, but not as pretty as me.

I'm sick of waiting for my boy to get off work.  

Julia's dog bit me, so I kicked it.

That chicken salad sandwich at Arby's is scrumptious.

I'm looking for a second job.  However, if I get one, I'll have to postpone school that much longer, and I don't want to do that.  I'm so going back next semester, and for free, since my dad wants to use me as a tax write-off.  I'm not complaining, because now I can get my stupid degree, and I don't even have to pay for it.

I saved lots of money, its awesome, but then again my credit card bill will probably decimate my next paycheck, not awesome.

Blah things to do bye

Things are excellent.

I missed quite a bit of work due to my stupid being sick-ness, and unfortunately I seem to be sick again, but I'm sure I'll live.  I'm supposed to be getting a raise soon, and that is always good.  I like almost everyone I work with.  My co-worker is having a party on Friday; I believe me and Tim will make an appearance.

I've been contemplating going vegetarian again, but everytime I try I get hungry and do something stupid like eat a cheeseburger.  This has got to stop, it is driving me nuts.  I just want to be un-fat again!  I have no willpower, I really don't.  

I haven't been hanging out with many people lately, but I have been enjoying my time alone.

I'm off to bed.

i have the flu, i am a puking sick mess, i haven't left my house in days.  somehow i have to work the rest of the week but i don't quite know how i'm going to manage that.  i called in twice this week already.

i haven't really seen anyone in a few days, i'm kind of lonely.  i miss my boyfriend and i miss my friends and i hate being sick arrrg!

i wish it was cold, its wayyy too hot in my house.
